hkgmoji\" />但無賣機票"},{"pid":"4c36f9262078dd8cdcd23fe3e6423ba4add486b6","tid":1679063,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyhY6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyhY6E.jpg&h=3c98bcf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pv6zgTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpv6zgTk.jpg&h=d35d8ec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7496163193da4de53acb65db0e807ed99c5ff582","tid":1679063,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"無一間大野係黃<br />\n<br />\n只有紅同藍 分別<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea36250fe54a5042b0931614a350a8fafd9bb262","tid":1679063,"uid":336350,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5xiJAs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5xiJAs.png&h=a9b801e1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}